[size=18pt][i][b]Upcoming Goals/Updates[/b][/i][/size]
The membership system is different, it's not a 'true or false', wether the player is a member or not!
In Rs2 it goes by days, ex: quick write up

[code]public boolean isMember(){
  if(memberDays > 0)
    return false
return true;
}[/code]

There's also an expiration date too. I plan on using the membership features for donators! I'm currently working on this PayPal IPN system so for anyone who donates gets 40 membership days and will expire at one point etc. 

